.0297, 168.4564, 169.8615, 168.3401, 167.8698, 168.1623, 167.0772, 166.2976, 166.7218, 166.3963, 166.8619, 166.3509, 165.6864, 165.5756, 166.2899, 165.0854, 164.2903, 163.8475, 164.3344, 165.0263, 165.1245, 165.8971, 166.2952, 166.2126, 167.2492, 168.3156, 168.6574, 169.5748, 169.7664, 170.1315, 170.2382, 170.2721, 168.9216, 169.4251, 169.5042, 169.7631, 169.528, 169.9321, 169.236, 168.929, 169.9933, 171.2034, 169.8435, 169.7293, 171.3203, 170.936, 170.6289, 171.2985, 171.3415, 170.1772, 169.5368, 169.573, 169.1352, 169.8026, 169.3697, 167.5985, 167.5313, 167.5458, 168.6945, 169.0232, 169.4801, 170.4824, 170.1344, 170.5584, 169.9743, 170.1727, 171.0522, 170.6169, 172.036, 171.516, 170.2639, 170.4339, 169.7079, 170.5563, 170.6513, 170.08, 170.5856, 170.52, 170.867, 170.0348, 171.722, 172.1303, 171.5232, 170.7116, 170.4475, 170.9374, 170.5719, 169.2244, 169.0912, 169.835, 169.4622, 170.3352, 171.0536, 172.4727, 171.7113, 171.7843, 171.6707, 170.37, 169.4784, 168.8976, 167.3949, 168.478, 169.5334, 167.4949, 168.832, 169.0853, 167.7954, 168.9582, 167.4273, 167.1486, 166.8528, 164.7001, 163.6662, 164.7754, 163.9345, 161.628, 164.1476, 164.4267, 163.3027, 166.1075, 165.7094, 165.1076, 165.2057, 165.8827, 163.3255, 164.945, 164.8472, 164.9056, 164.3234, 167.6631, 165.7998, 164.6612, 164.7158, 166.892, 166.5115, 166.2414, 167.06, 166.275, 165.8323, 166.6472, 166.1733, 164.434, 164.4124, 164.8199, 170.6175, 177.0743, 174.9205, 178.1656, 179.795, 184.2041, 179.5742, 181.3111, 183.3964, 183.4162, 185.7106, 186.3968, 189.077, 194.1012, 190.3627, 187.7562, 188.0945, 185.9216, 187.259, 187.0406, 187.1276, 187.2284, 186.9581], "summary_html": "<h1>GP遗传规划截面因子 | Sharpe 1.254 | 通过</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略复现中信期货利用遗传规划(Genetic Programming)在商品期货截面上挖掘的5个alpha因子。GP通过对OHLCV、持仓量、仓单等11个原始特征进行时序算子嵌套组合（如滚动均值、标准差、RSI、KAMA、相关系数、协方差等），自动搜索出具有截面选期能力的复合公式树。5个因子分别捕捉了量价相关性振荡(Alpha1)、仓单极值归一化(Alpha2)、持仓量自适应均线RSI(Alpha3)、量价相关稳定性(Alpha4)、开盘价与成交量协方差(Alpha5)。每日对因子值进行截面排名，做多高分组、做空低分组，构建多空组合。</p>\n<p>策略赚钱的核心逻辑：多因子等权组合（排除了表现最差的Alpha1）可以从多维度捕捉商品期货截面价值差异，通过截面标准化(CS)归一化进一步增强信号稳定性，不同因子间低相关性提供了分散化收益。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.0</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.0%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-6.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.14</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.48</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.4 / 0.96</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.04</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.09</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.35</span></td><td>1.23</td><td>1.17</td><td>1.77</td><td>0.36</td><td>0.77</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.87</span></td><td>1.13</td><td>1.84</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.1</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.01</span></td><td>1.19</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.51</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>open</code></td><td>开盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>vwap</code></td><td>VWAP</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 7 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 7 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>5个因子的GP公式树：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha1} = \\text{ts\\_midpoint}\\big(\\text{ts\\_pct\\_change}\\big(\\text{ts\\_inverse\\_cv}\\big(\\text{ts\\_AROONOSC}(V, P_{vwap}, 10), 10\\big), 5\\big), 486\\big) \\quad (\\text{正向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha2} = \\text{ts\\_sum}\\big(\\text{ts\\_maxmin}\\big(\\text{ts\\_maxmin}(W, 126), 126\\big), 63\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha3} = \\text{ts\\_ema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_sum}\\big(\\text{ts\\_rsi}\\big(\\text{ts\\_kama}(OI, 486), 63\\big), 243\\big), 63\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha4} = \\text{ts\\_ema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_inverse\\_cv}\\big(\\text{ts\\_corr}(V, P_{vwap}, 21), 42\\big), 105\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha5} = \\text{ts\\_dema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_median}\\big(\\text{ts\\_cov}(P_{open}, V, 21), 21\\big), 15\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<p>其中：<span class=\"math-tex\">V</span> = volume, <span class=\"math-tex\">P_{vwap}</span> = vwap, <span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> = receipt(仓单), <span class=\"math-tex\">OI</span> = opi(持仓量), <span class=\"math-tex\">P_{open}</span> = open</p>\n<p><strong>关键算子定义</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li><code>ts_inverse_cv(X, d)</code> = rolling_mean(X,d) / rolling_std(X,d)</li>\n<li><code>ts_maxmin(X, d)</code> = (X - rolling_min(X,d)) / (rolling_max(X,d) - rolling_min(X,d))</li>\n<li><code>ts_AROONOSC(X1, X2, d)</code> = Aroon振荡器（近似：两变量在窗口内的相对位置差）</li>\n<li><code>ts_kama(X, d)</code> = Kaufman自适应移动均线</li>\n<li><code>ts_dema(X, d)</code> = 2*EMA(X,d) - EMA(EMA(X,d),d)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>组合信号</strong>: Combo = 等权平均(Alpha2_rank, Alpha3_rank, Alpha4_rank, Alpha5_rank)，截面标准化后做多空。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p>1. <strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.98)</strong>: 实现全部5个GP因子，Alpha2(仓单极值)最强(0.98)，Alpha1(Aroon)反向(-0.45)。诊断发现combo有潜力但受Alpha1拖累。 - 诊断: Alpha1 Aroon振荡器近似不够准确，或方向判断有误 - 行动: 计划R2排除Alpha1，聚焦combo和Alpha2</p>\n<p>2. <strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.21)</strong>: 排除Alpha1后的4因子combo+截面标准化(CS)大幅提升。combo_H5_cs达1.21，比单因子alpha2(0.98)提升24%。CS归一化普遍优于raw和ts。 - 诊断: CS归一化明显有效，hold期可进一步优化 - 行动: R3扩展hold期搜索，加IC门控</p>\n<p>3. <strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.25)</strong>: Hold=7天略优于5天(1.254 vs 1.213)，IC门控未带来额外提升（combo已足够稳定）。多个变体Sharpe&gt;1.0，信号稳健。 - 关键转折: 从单因子Alpha2到4因子combo+CS归一化，Sharpe从0.98提升至1.25</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（58个有效品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 7天换仓（最优），1-10天均可</li>\n<li><strong>信号类型</strong>: 截面多空</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - Alpha2依赖仓单数据(receipt)，该字段非空率约28%，部分品种缺失时因子退化\n<p>- Alpha1(Aroon振荡器)在本实现中表现为负，可能因Aroon算子的近似偏差 - 年度Sharpe分布不均：2016-2017和2020表现最强，2023-2024略弱 - 高杠杆(CS归一化后名义杠杆&gt;1x)贡献了部分收益</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9989</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.79s</li>\n</ul>"}